property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hm? Confused why a heavily customized Navi is down here? Well if you must know, I was sent here to learn more about this rumour of "Crimson" being somewhere in the Undernet, luckily it was just a false alarm. Heh, Perhaps you understand what I'm really talking about. Huh, Why haven't I left yet? Well to be honest I'm just enjoying the music. I'm more of a neoclassical guy myself, but I'd be lying if this music didn't get me pumped up!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Heya! How did you get up here? Eh no matter, welcome to my HP! Anyone is welcome here; especially the ugliest and baddest Navis! You're pretty brave to even be speaking to me right now...Say; did you know I used to be an Offical? I retired after my 30 years of service. It's nice to kick back, and enjoy life ya know? Who knows? Maybe I'll find trouble makers, and put their face in the dirt!~ Maybe I'll even feel like battling you too! When I'm feelin it you WILL know!
